Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:02.94,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的夜晚  也不能停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:07.94,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始前行  等待着那份炽热
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:13.07,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦肩而过的心完美地没有交汇点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:18.08,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那距黎明还遥遥无期的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:23.08,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们比隆冬的寒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:27.84,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加痴迷 虚幻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:32.93,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中沉淀的那份雪白的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:37.97,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐涌溢  摇动我的坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:43.40,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是天空撒下的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:48.61,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是雪花凝结而成的羽翼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.99,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.12,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着那仅存的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:05.09,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧拥抱着你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:02.94,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,itetuku yoru tatitomarezu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:07.94,SonglmOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bokura hajimaru netu wo matteru
